<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sell Book | Colorful Design</title>
    <style>
        /* --- 1. RESET --- */
        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
            height: 100vh;
            overflow: hidden;
            background: #f0f2f5; /* Light background for contrast */
        }

        /* --- 2. SPLIT LAYOUT CONTAINER --- */
        .container {
            display: flex;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        /* --- 3. LEFT SIDE (MULTI-COLOR + TEXT) --- */
        .left-panel {
            flex: 1.1; /* Thoda zyada jagah lega */
            
            /* ðŸ”¥ MULTI-COLOR GRADIENT (OFFLINE) */
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4f46e5 0%, #9333ea 50%, #ec4899 100%);
            
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 60px;
            color: white;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        /* Decorative Circles (Background Design) */
        .circle {
            position: absolute;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }
        .c1 { width: 300px; height: 300px; top: -50px; left: -50px; }
        .c2 { width: 200px; height: 200px; bottom: 50px; right: -50px; }
        .c3 { width: 100px; height: 100px; top: 40%; right: 20%; opacity: 0.5; }

        /* Left Content Text */
        .left-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out;
        }

        .tagline {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 5px 15px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .left-content h1 {
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: 800;
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .left-content p {
            font-size: 18px;
            opacity: 0.9;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            max-width: 450px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Features List */
        .features {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .feature-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .icon-box {
            width: 40px; height: 40px;
            background: white;
            color: #9333ea;
            border-radius: 10px;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            margin-right: 15px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        /* --- 4. RIGHT SIDE (FORM) --- */
        .right-panel {
            flex: 0.9;
            background: #ffffff;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 40px;
            overflow-y: auto;
        }

        .form-wrapper { width: 100%; max-width: 450px; }

        h2 { color: #111; font-size: 30px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 5px; }
        .subtitle { color: #666; margin-bottom: 30px; font-size: 14px; }

        /* Inputs */
        .form-group { margin-bottom: 20px; }
        label { display: block; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: 13px; color: #333; }
        
        input, select {
            width: 100%; padding: 14px;
            border: 2px solid #eee; border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 15px; background: #fafafa;
            transition: 0.3s; outline: none;
        }
        input:focus, select:focus { border-color: #9333ea; background: #fff; }

        .row { display: flex; gap: 15px; }
        .col { flex: 1; }

        /* File Upload */
        .file-box {
            border: 2px dashed #ccc; padding: 20px;
            text-align: center; border-radius: 10px;
            cursor: pointer; background: #f9f9f9; position: relative;
        }
        .file-box:hover { border-color: #9333ea; background: #f3e8ff; }

        button {
            width: 100%; padding: 16px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #4f46e5, #9333ea);
            color: white; border: none; border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.3s; margin-top: 10px;
        }
        button:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(147, 51, 234, 0.3); }

        .cancel { display: block; text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; color: #888; text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px; }

        /* --- 5. MOBILE RESPONSIVE --- */
        @media (max-width: 900px) {
            .left-panel { display: none; } /* Mobile pe colorful side gayab */
            .right-panel { flex: 1; }
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        
        <div class="left-panel">
            <div class="circle c1"></div>
            <div class="circle c2"></div>
            <div class="circle c3"></div>

            <div class="left-content">
                <div class="tagline">Welcome to Campus Store</div>
                <h1>Turn Your Books<br>Into Cash. ðŸ“šðŸ’¸</h1>
                <p>Helping students save money. List your old semester books today and connect with juniors instantly.</p>

                <div class="features">
                    <div class="feature-item">
                        <div class="icon-box">âš¡</div>
                        <div>
                            <strong>Fast Selling</strong><br>
                            <span style="font-size: 13px; opacity: 0.8;">Most books sell within 24 hours.</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-item">
                        <div class="icon-box">ðŸ’¬</div>
                        <div>
                            <strong>Direct Chat</strong><br>
                            <span style="font-size: 13px; opacity: 0.8;">Connect via WhatsApp instantly.</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-item">
                        <div class="icon-box">ðŸ”’</div>
                        <div>
                            <strong>100% Free</strong><br>
                            <span style="font-size: 13px; opacity: 0.8;">No hidden charges or commissions.</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="right-panel">
            <div class="form-wrapper">
                <h2>Sell a Book</h2>
                <p class="subtitle">Fill in the details to create a listing.</p>

                <form action="/save-book" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">
                    
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>Book Name</label>
                        <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="E.g. Database Systems" required>
                    </div>

                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col form-group">
                            <label>Author</label>
                            <input type="text" name="author" placeholder="E.g. Korth" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col form-group">
                            <label>Price (â‚¹)</label>
                            <input type="number" name="price" placeholder="450" required>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>WhatsApp Number</label>
                        <input type="number" name="contact" placeholder="9876543210" required>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>Branch / Category</label>
                        <select name="branch" required>
                            <option value="" disabled selected>Select Branch</option>
                            <option value="General">General / Common</option>
                            <option value="CSE">Computer Science (CSE)</option>
                            <option value="Mechanical">Mechanical</option>
                            <option value="Civil">Civil</option>
                            <option value="Electrical">Electrical</option>
                            <option value="BBA_MBA">BBA / MBA</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label>Book Photo</label>
                        <div class="file-box">
                            <span id="ftext" style="color:#666; font-size:14px;">Click to Upload Image</span>
                            <input type="file" name="image" required accept="image/*" 
                                   style="position: absolute; top:0; left:0; width:100%; height:100%; opacity:0; cursor:pointer;"
                                   onchange="document.getElementById('ftext').innerText = this.files[0].name">
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <button type="submit">Publish Listing</button>
                    <a href="/" class="cancel">Cancel & Go Back</a>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

</body>
</html>